-- that the party could do
better than it's

41:53.311 --> 41:54.512 align:left position:37.5%,start line:93.33% size:62.5%
done.

41:54.545 --> 41:56.814 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
CHARLES PETERS: It's let the
