in that respect.

41:56.848 --> 42:01.486 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
But I am still a Democrat, proud
to be a Democrat.

42:01.519 --> 42:05.056 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
I -- on the whole, we're on the
right side.

42:05.089 --> 42:11.295 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
But in these two ways of getting
too involved
with making money ourselves --
we're too involved

42:11.329 --> 42:14.932 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
in thinking we're a little bit
better than
the other guy.

42:14.966 --> 42:19.971 align:left position:25%,start line:73.33% size:75%
When they were
environmentalists, they didn't
think, whose jobs are this going
to cost?

42:20.004 --> 42:24.442 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
If they worked for a certain
trade policy,
