going to cost,

42:24.475 --> 42:28.613 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
and what can I do to help those
people this
is going to hurt?

42:28.646 --> 42:30.615 align:left position:12.5%,start line:80% size:87.5%
JUDY WOODRUFF: It's an
indictment of Hillary
Clinton.

42:30.648 --> 42:31.783 align:left position:12.5%,start line:93.33% size:87.5%
CHARLES PETERS: Yes.

42:31.816 --> 42:33.584 align:left position:12.5%,start line:93.33% size:87.5%
Unfortunately, yes.

42:33.618 --> 42:37.922 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
The key symbolic thing that is
going to happen
