conspicuous

42:52.837 --> 42:54.972 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
consumption that are sinking
this country.

42:55.006 --> 42:56.774 align:left position:0%,start line:93.33% size:100%
JUDY WOODRUFF: You're 90.

42:56.808 --> 43:01.446 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
The book is a story of the last
half-century
